  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promoting Fundamental Principles and Rights at Work</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed project will seek to address these challenges in both law and practice by facilitating an improved legal framework in conformity with ILS and in particular C87 and C98; enhancing the freedom and capacity of workers and their representatives to exercise their rights in practice; and improving labour-management cooperation at the enterprise level. The implementation of this project will contribute to build a solid ground that will ensure the successful implementation of a potential fully fledge Better Work programme in Bangladesh.</narrative>
  </description>
